<item>
            <title>[LU-2955] replay-ost-single 8b: Hung until Autotest timed out</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-2955</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;This issue was created by maloo for Li Wei &amp;lt;liwei@whamcloud.com&amp;gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;This issue relates to the following test suite run: &lt;a href=&quot;https://maloo.whamcloud.com/test_sets/2124fdda-8b27-11e2-965f-52540035b04c&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;https://maloo.whamcloud.com/test_sets/2124fdda-8b27-11e2-965f-52540035b04c&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;The sub-test test_8b failed with the following error:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;blockquote&gt;
&lt;p&gt;test failed to respond and timed out&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/blockquote&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Info required for matching: replay-ost-single 8b&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;No better log pattern for matching.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Originally, I thought it had something to do with my &lt;a href=&quot;http://review.whamcloud.com/5667&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;http://review.whamcloud.com/5667&lt;/a&gt;, but it turned out this happened also without that patch:&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://maloo.whamcloud.com/test_sets/6d1cb8dc-8ba8-11e2-aa89-52540035b04c&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;https://maloo.whamcloud.com/test_sets/6d1cb8dc-8ba8-11e2-aa89-52540035b04c&lt;/a&gt;&lt;br/&gt;
&lt;a href=&quot;https://maloo.whamcloud.com/test_sets/35660f84-8bb1-11e2-aa89-52540035b04c&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;https://maloo.whamcloud.com/test_sets/35660f84-8bb1-11e2-aa89-52540035b04c&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;All failures (4/4) I had seen was on ZFS.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
